g/resource/Francis_I_of_France\", \"score\": 0.7732650925416613, \"rank\": 0.25704945630385, \"text\": \"Francis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_I_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_I_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"KINGSTON\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 8}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 100m\", \"from\": 73, \"to\": 87}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 108}, {\"ngram\": \"the unusually lengthy wait\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 224}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 238}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The start of the final, held in front of a capacity crowd of over 75,000, was delayed for an unusually long time before American Noah Lyles edged out Thompson by the closest margin ever-5/1000ths of a second-after both men crossed the finish line in 9.79 seconds.\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 397, \"end\": 405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9991634921729987, \"rank\": 0.0008304798644317322, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 427, \"end\": 435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9925899492563673, \"rank\": 0.007465369313722229, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The start\", \"