, \"from\": 728, \"to\": 744}, {\"ngram\": \"the hour\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"45 minutes\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"break\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 812}, {\"ngram\": \"the bigger issue\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think his problem occurred when he came back after the semi-finals with a hamstring issue, and from our perspective, we had to spend the entire time trying to get him ready to run, or at least to participate, because based on what he said he was feeling, it was uncertain,\\\" Francis said.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_I_of_France\", \"score\": 0.7732650925416613, \"rank\": 0.25704945630385, \"text\": \"Francis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_I_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_I_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his problem\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 868}, {\"ngram\": \"the semi\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"a hamstring issue\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"our perspective\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire time\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The physiotherapist, Francis toldObserver Online, \\\"had to use all kinds of techniques to not only get him okay, but to make him believe he was okay.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The physiotherapist\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1159}, {\"ngram\": \"toldObserver\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1181}, {\"ngram\": \"all kinds\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"techniques\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the warm-up, before they went to the call room, I had intended to emphasise the start because I knew that was crucial, but we could not do it because we did not want to encourage him to push out from the blocks and get himself hurt.\\\"\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1525, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the warm-up\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"the call room\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"the blocks\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Francis, who had argued before the start of the Olympics that experience would not be a factor for Thompson in his first major championships, admitted that the athlete might have been affected more by the unplanned delay than the other men.\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1527, \"end\": 1534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_I_of_France\", \"score\": 0.7732650925416613, \"rank\": 0.25704945630385, \"text\": \"Francis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_I_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_I_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1626, \"end\": 1634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9925899492563673, \"rank\": 0.007465369313722229, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"a factor\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"his first major championships\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1667}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"the unplanned delay\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"the other men\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think they [the officials] did what they had to do,\\\" Francis said, \\\"But as I told Kishane, I said, 'Kishane, they did what they needed to do; you should have done what you needed to do, which was just to leave the start line.\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1825, \"end\": 1832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_I_of_France\", \"score\": 0.7732650925416613, \"rank\": 0.25704945630385, \"text\": \"Francis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_I_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_I_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the officials\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1797}, {\"ngram\": \"Kishane\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"the start line\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You should have left the line, gone out there, and told them that when they are ready, they can call you back.\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But you should not have allowed them to have you standing there for seven minutes.'\\\"\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2193, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"seven minutes\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Francis said, \\\"I would not really call it a big a factor.\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2261, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_I_of_France\", \"score\": 0.7732650925416613, \"rank\": 0.25704945630385, \"text\": \"Francis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_I_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_I_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big a factor\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean it probably affecting him a little bit more, because he was not used to it, because these kinds of pauses occur on the circuit, sometimes not as long, and they tend to occur at the big championship sometimes, but I have never seen so long but I do not think he knew how to handle that kind of stuff as well.\\\"\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2577, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these kinds\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2364}, {\"ngram\": \"pauses\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2374}, {\"ngram\": \"the circuit\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2395}, {\"ngram\": \"the big championship\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2466}, {\"ngram\": \"that kind\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2558}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"- Paul A Reid Tags: HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2612, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"- Paul A Reid Tags\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2610}]}]}"